## Developer Guide

If you are new to using `nbdev` here are some useful pointers to get you
started.

### Install string_therapy in Development mode

``` sh
# make sure string_therapy package is installed in development mode
$ pip install -e .

# make changes under nbs/ directory
# ...

# compile to have changes apply to string_therapy
$ nbdev_prepare
```

## Usage

### Installation

Install latest from the GitHub
[repository](https://github.com/alix559/string_therapy):

``` sh
$ pip install git+https://github.com/alix559/string_therapy.git
```

or from [conda](https://anaconda.org/alix559/string_therapy)

``` sh
$ conda install -c alix559 string_therapy
```

or from [pypi](https://pypi.org/project/string_therapy/)

``` sh
$ pip install string_therapy
```

